{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-types-post-js","path":"/levels-of-autonomous-driving/","result":{"data":{"post":{"id":"cG9zdDoxMDgy","uri":"/levels-of-autonomous-driving/","excerpt":"<p>Driver assisted technologies, driverless technology, robotic cars, autonomous vehicles…  If all the different talk and types of autonomous driving has you a bit confused you’re not alone.  In this iDriveSoCal [&hellip;]</p>\n","content":"<p>Driver assisted technologies, driverless technology, robotic cars, autonomous vehicles…  If all the different talk and types of autonomous driving has you a bit confused you’re not alone.  In this iDriveSoCal Podcast we lay out the six Automation Levels as described by the Society of Automotive Engineers and accepted by the National Highway Traffic Safety Administration.  And yes there are six levels, not five, listen to get all the details.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.nhtsa.gov/technology-innovation/automated-vehicles-safety\">National Highway Traffic Safety Administration: Automated Safety for Vehicles</a></p>\n<p><span class=\"alignnone wp-image-1083 size-full inline-gatsby-image-wrapper gatsby-image-wrapper\" style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;width:1200px\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width:100%;padding-bottom:31.666666666666668%\"></span><img aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:0;transition-delay:500ms\"/><picture><source srcSet=\"/static/c3bf8ebef9bdecd2eaabe95c0ee858fc/f2d49/iDSC043-Banner.png 300w,\n/static/c3bf8ebef9bdecd2eaabe95c0ee858fc/ff59c/iDSC043-Banner.png 600w,\n/static/c3bf8ebef9bdecd2eaabe95c0ee858fc/5ece7/iDSC043-Banner.png 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"/><img sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" srcSet=\"/static/c3bf8ebef9bdecd2eaabe95c0ee858fc/f2d49/iDSC043-Banner.png 300w,\n/static/c3bf8ebef9bdecd